The Dark Avians hollow halls began to emit noise. "Emergency, Emergency,
uknown signatures within range of base. Select course of actions." it
informed the base. Megatron snarled. To much was going on at one time,
he opened a com-link. "Triggerhappy, Skullgrin, Blindchaos, head towards
the pods, I will meet you there." he said over it. He then turned to
Dominjoe and Blind Chaos. "Nevermind, you will have your first test in
the field." he said calmly, pointing to them to follow him." He headed
towards the exit. "Computer, innitiate defence system in two cycles." he
commanded.
